#. Paragraph text in the Getting Started SeminaryERP Workspace
#: seminary/seminary/workspace/getting_started_seminaryerp/getting_started_seminaryerp.json
msgid "Each student created automatically creates a customer, but you may want to create other customers for churches who want to pay part of the tuition of their pastors, etc. Then, you can assign more payers for an individual program enrollment (e.g., student and church will be invoiced separately if you so choose). Scholarships should be used for those sponsored by the Seminary (e.g., from donations to a fund/cost-center that the seminary has freedom to manage).&nbsp;"
msgstr "Cada estudiante creado crea automáticamente un cliente, pero puede que quiera crear otros clientes para iglesias que deseen pagar parte de la matrícula de sus pastores, etc. Luego, podrá asignar más pagadores para una inscripción individual al programa (p. ej., estudiante e iglesia serán facturados por separado si así lo elige). Las becas deben usarse para quienes estén patrocinados por el Seminario (p. ej., a partir de donaciones a un fondo/centro de costos que el seminario tenga libertad para administrar).&nbsp;"

